## Form Output

All action elements integrate with FormDown's **Hidden Form Architecture**:

```html
<!-- Generated HTML -->
<form hidden id="formdown-form-1" action="/register" method="POST"></form>

<div class="formdown-field-container">
  <input type="text" name="name" form="formdown-form-1" required>
</div>

<div class="formdown-field-container">
  <button type="submit" form="formdown-form-1" class="btn btn-primary">
    Send Message
  </button>
</div>
```

This ensures clean styling without form wrapper interference! ‚ú®